id=apex-root
name=APEX-Root Unidirectional Hide
version=v1.1.1
versionCode=125
author=APEX-Root Team
description=Unidirectional transparent root hiding: only APEX-Root sees real root status, all others see 100% clean system. Supports eBPF firewall (Android 12+) + legacy mount-ns/LD_PRELOAD fallback (Android 10-11). One-click switch between Detection / Hide / Game modes.
